name: LibyaConnect

description: Online marketplace for trade with Libya
overview:
LibyaConnect is an online business-to-business marketplace where buyers in Libya and sellers to Libya are encouraged to meet, engage and conduct business.

Its primary aim is to ensure that buyers of goods and services in this great country are finally able to benefit from the competitiveness, efficiency and transparency of a business community without boundaries.

As a result, it gives small and medium sized local businesses the greatest chance for prosperity by supporting them to buy at the best price, get the highest quality, with the right schedule.

Founded by a team with both intricate local Libyan business knowledge and extensive international commercial experience, the plan is to position this marketplace as the must-go-to online destination for trade in and with Libya.

Combine the best of Alibaba with the best of LinkedIn but all tailored to Libyan commerce.
